<h2>The Bottom Line</h2>

<p>
  Cozy Couples and OurCouple are cut from the same cloth — cozy, gamified, made for two. Cozy goes deeper on decorating a shared home; OurCouple goes deeper on daily rituals, a real memory journal, compatibility games and privacy. You won't go wrong either way — pick the one whose daily loop you'll actually keep up, together.
